<body>
    <button class="theme-toggle" aria-label="Toggle theme" id="themeBtn">🌙</button>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Wapp</h1>
        <p>
            Wapp is a fast, secure, and beautifully minimal messaging app.<br>
            Experience seamless communication with privacy-first features and a stunning interface.
